=== Uses ===

Install {{Package|app-shells/dash}}:
{{USEflag
|libedit
|static
}}

=== Emerge ===

{{emerge|dash}}

== Configuration ==

To make dash the default shell:
{{Cmd|chsh -s /bin/dash}}

